    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1898-03-04T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1898-03-04T00:00:00-05:00" n="539"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d539">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Day</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Woodford</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-03-04">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 4, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Spanish chargé presented here yesterday matter covered in yours 3d. Explained to
                    him that vessels are the <hi rend="italic">Montgomery</hi> and <hi rend="italic"
                        >Nashville</hi>, small cruiser and gunboat. <hi rend="italic"
                        >Montgomery</hi> has called at Cuban ports recently. At request relief
                    committee these ships will take load of supplies Key West to Matanzas and Sagua
                    next week. This is the most prompt and efficient means of getting supplies to
                    people greatly in need.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Day.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
